name: Gainfull
description: Gainfull ecosystem is a galaxy of sub-projects, including Metaverse, an exchange platform, NFT marketplace, and share pools. The project was created with an eye to uniting traders and investors. "Gainfull's main goal is to provide extra income for our community while they are predicting token prices. Users will benefit from the vast experience of Gainfull's core team members while improving their trading skills every day. With an active community of over 5K people, you'll feel like close trading friends earning every time," the team stated.
